DP array build up solution: (This is Widely regarded as a DP problem, and I agree, the pattern is Definitely there.  That said, this isn't even close to the optimal solution.  But, it's recognizable, and will likely carry you through an interview pretty well.  Cheers.)
```
const lengthOfLIS = nums => {
  let sequence = Array(nums.length).fill(1);
  for (let i = 0; i <= nums.length; i++) {
    for (let j = i - 1; j >= 0; j--) {
      if (nums[j] < nums[i]) sequence[i] = Math.max(sequence[i], sequence[j] + 1);
    }
  }
  return Math.max(...sequence)
}
```

